{"tid":864746,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蛆國又贏，將以正確的聖經　取代舊聖經","createTime":"2018-10-16T12:04:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T15:28:44.000Z","uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4d63fddac98d66ccc04b5ffd2ebcb36c1697021a","tid":864746,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T12:04:39.000Z","msg":"隨著當局打壓基督教力道增加，中國網購平台也悄悄將《聖經》等宗教經典下架。（法新社） <br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕即便中國近年對境內基督徒進行大規模迫害，天主教教宗方濟各仍於22日與中國達成主教任命協議，引來國際輿論熱議，美國舊金山一名牧師日前公開表示，中國政府將重新編訂《聖經》，其中會加入儒家、道家及佛家經典，並在註釋本中體現愛黨愛國的「社會主義價值觀」。 <br />\n<br />\n根據美國《自由亞洲電台》報導，美國舊金山「華人基督徒公義團契」創辦人劉貽牧師，日前公開演說時表示，中國政府將重新編訂及註釋《聖經》，新編的《中華基督教聖經》將加入儒家、道家及佛家經典篇章，註釋部分則會引入愛國、愛黨思想，以體現社會主義核心價值觀。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2564207\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2564207&d=cUe2kGK3L7mzwis%2B9D76sU4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=b7e548f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2564207&h=2226c308\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2564207</a>"},{"pid":"834feaccc410c144c3b507384e243c1ea595f41e","tid":864746,"uid":33643,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T12:04:57.000Z","msg":"大家請記住：<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">連登乞衣樓豬---EDO脆餅#23833<br />\n(被追擊後第&ldquo;5&rdquo;個新名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：玩到你精神病）</span><br />\n<br />\n想買不死鳥風褸，點買先最抵？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/504716/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/504716/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n乞衣仔經典語錄:<br />\n<br />\n&quot;<em><span style=\"color: blue;\">我：你食撚左飯未<br />\n你： 我食左屎啦 </span></em>&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n乞衣仔你上水未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"